    "body": "# Summary\r\n\r\nTVM FFI allows passing `torch.Tensor` directly at runtime instead of `from_dlpack` conversion on every call, reducing launch overhead (~0.5μs per call per NVIDIA docs). Lets see if thats true :)\r\n\r\n## What Works\r\n- Simple forward pass (non-varlen, non-paged, no block sparsity, no aux tensors)\r\n- `None` optional arguments need some shenanigans  (cutlass DSL 4.3.1+)\r\n- Backward pass works works \r\n\r\n## Known Issues / warts\r\n\r\n`**Blocker**`: Optional args dont seem to be working (at least as I expect) they seem to need to be all None or maybe all not None but no mixed. Following up with some folks\r\n\r\n1. No kwargs at runtime\r\n```python\r\n# Fails: compiled_fn(..., mdQ_semaphore=value)\r\n# Works: compiled_fn(..., value)  # positional only\r\n```\r\n\r\n2. BlockSparseTensors NamedTuple not supported\r\n```\r\nDSLRuntimeError: Unsupported argument type: <class 'BlockSparseTensors'>\r\n```\r\nTVM FFI arg spec converter can't handle custom NamedTuples - reported to cute folks\r\n\r\n## TODO\r\n\r\n### 1. Restructure compilation flow\r\nCurrently calling `from_dlpack` every invocation even on cache hit. Should:\r\n- Check cache first\r\n- Only convert tensors if compilation needed\r\n- Pass torch tensors directly on cache hit\r\n\r\n### 2. Use `make_fake_compact_tensor`\r\nFor compilation, use fake tensors with symbolic shapes (per CUTLASS examples) instead of real tensor conversion. Claims this is better perf and kind of get AOT for freeish\r\n\r\n### 3. Debug ICE issues\r\nInvestigate LLVM operand count mismatches in certain kernel configurations.\r\n\r\n### 4. BlockSparseTensors\r\nEither wait for NVIDIA NamedTuple support or restructure to pass individual tensors.\r\n\r\n\r\n### Is it worth it\r\n\r\n## Before:\r\nHot loop after 5 runs of warmup:\r\n\r\n<img width=\"758\" height=\"345\" alt=\"Screenshot 2025-12-02 at 7 51 32 PM\" src=\"https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/655ec5bc-764e-4177-8236-f091cf06e885\" />\r\n\r\n## After (this pr)\r\n<img width=\"783\" height=\"333\" alt=\"Screenshot 2025-12-02 at 7 50 09 PM\" src=\"https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/b383db86-8320-4cbf-9045-f61e16f12a24\" />\r\n\r\n\r\n### Manually timing with perf counter since with-stack skews kinda heavily\r\n## Before on Main\r\n```\r\nPhase                                                Time (us)\r\n--------------------------------------------------  -----------\r\nInput Validation & Setup (Contiguity, Shapes)           70.489\r\nMetadata DLPack Conversion                              12.492\r\nBlock Sparsity Tensor Prep                               0.315\r\nMetadata Extraction & Tensor Layout                      9.832\r\nHeuristics (Split-KV, Block Sizes)                       0.488\r\nMain Tensor DLPack Conversion                           31.612\r\nHashing Score/Mask Mods                                  0.413\r\nCompilation Cache Key Generation                         0.536\r\nCompilation Check & Kernel Launch                       52.892\r\nTotal Interface Overhead                               193.359\r\n```\r\n\r\n\r\n## With this PR\r\n```\r\nPhase                                                Time (us)\r\n--------------------------------------------------  -----------\r\nInput Validation & Setup (Contiguity, Shapes)           63.269\r\nMetadata Extraction & Tensor Layout                     14.190\r\nHeuristics (Split-KV, Block Sizes)                       0.526\r\nHashing Score/Mask Mods                                  0.298\r\nBlock Sparsity Tensor Prep                               0.341\r\nCompilation Cache Key Generation                         0.569\r\nMain Tensor DLPack Conversion                            0.605\r\nCompilation Check & Kernel Launch                       12.349\r\nTotal Interface Overhead                               105.357\r\n❯ \r\n```\r\n\r\nSo in line w/ ~2x reduction in cpu time\r\n\r\nPhase | Lines | Description\r\n-- | -- | --\r\nInput Validation & Setup | 229-366 | Contiguity checks, shape extraction, dtype assertions, output tensor allocation\r\nMetadata Extraction & Tensor Layout | 370-386 | Causal/local flags, window size handling, CUDA stream\r\nHeuristics (Split-KV, Block Sizes) | 390-425 | Block size tuning, pack_gqa decisions, num_splits heuristic\r\nHashing Score/Mask Mods | 429-437 | utils.hash_callable() for score_mod/mask_mod\r\nBlock Sparsity Tensor Prep | 441-476 | Varlen checks, block sparsity validation (near-zero when not using flex)\r\nCompilation Cache Key Generation | 481-509 | Building the compile_key tuple\r\nMain Tensor DLPack Conversion | 514-567 | from_dlpack() + .detach() calls (only runs on cache miss)\r\nCompilation Check & Kernel Launch | 572-647 | Cache lookup + cute.compile() (if miss) + kernel invocation\r\n\r\n",
